        <h2>Estate and Trust Services</h2>
        <ul>
            <li><strong>Estate Planning:</strong> Comprehensive strategies for wealth transfer, including wills, trusts, and powers of attorney.</li>
            <li><strong>Trust Administration:</strong> Managing revocable and irrevocable trusts, ensuring compliance with trust terms and tax obligations.</li>
            <li><strong>Succession Planning:</strong> Advising on business succession to maintain control and minimize tax impact.</li>
            <li><strong>Probate Services:</strong> Guidance through the probate process to settle estates efficiently.</li>
            <li><strong>Charitable Giving:</strong> Designing and implementing charitable trusts or foundations that fulfill client wishes while offering tax advantages.</li>
        </ul>
    </div>

